    <string name="faq_what_is_dailybook_premium">What is DailyBook Pro?</string>
    <string name="faq_what_is_dailybook_premium_answer">DailyBook Pro unlocks extra features like ad-free experience, automatic monthly reports, data backup, and priority support. It helps you manage staff faster and more securely.</string>
    <string name="faq_how_does_autopay_work">How does Autopay work?</string>
    <string name="faq_how_does_autopay_work_answer">Autopay allows you to automatically renew your Pro plan every month or year using your UPI, debit card, or credit card. You don\'t have to pay manually each time — renewal happens safely and instantly.</string>
    <string name="faq_can_i_cancel_autopay">Can I cancel Autopay anytime?</string>
    <string name="faq_can_i_cancel_autopay_answer">Absolutely. You can cancel Autopay anytime from your UPI app (like PhonePe, Google Pay, Paytm, etc.) or directly from the DailyBook Pro settings. No hidden charges.</string>
    <string name="faq_what_happens_if_autopay_fails">What happens if my Autopay fails or I have low balance?</string>
    <string name="faq_what_happens_if_autopay_fails_answer">If your Autopay fails, we\'ll notify you instantly and give you the option to retry manually. Your Pro features will stay active for a short grace period so your data and access remain safe.</string>
    
